# Environment variables (Vite + server)

Copy to `.env` and fill in as needed.

| Variable | Purpose |
|----------|---------|
| `ERPNEXT_API_URL` | Frappe/ERPNext site base URL (trailing slash OK), e.g. `https://abledelali.l.frappe.cloud/` |
| `ERPNEXT_API_KEY` / `ERPNEXT_API_SECRET` | API token pair from ERPNext **Settings → Integrations → API Access** |
| `VITE_ERPNEXT_PUBLIC_URL` | Same host as ERPNext, **no** trailing slash — used for public blog image URLs in the browser |
| `ERPNEXT_HOMEPAGE_ROUTE` | Web Page **route** for Page Builder homepage copy (default `homepage`). |
| `ERPNEXT_ABOUT_ROUTE` | Web Page **route** for the React **`/about`** Page Builder copy (default `about-page`; avoids ERPNext’s stock `about` route). |
| `ERPNEXT_PUBLIC_VOICE_ROUTE` | Web Page **route** for the React **`/speaking-and-media`** Page Builder copy — one **Outreach** block (default `public-voice-page`). |
| `ERPNEXT_BOOKS_IS_FREE_FIELD` | (Optional) API name of the **Check** field for “free on site” / newsletter gift selection if not `is_free`. |
| `ERPNEXT_BLOG_PUBLISHED_FIELD` | (Optional) API name of the **Published** checkbox on **Blog Post** if not `published`. |
